features: POCKET&EXPANDING FILE FOLDERS: Skydue file organizer equipped with 5 pockets file folder, 2 pockets individual folder, 4 tab positions, and 8 colored label stickers

LARGE CAPACITY: Each File Folder size is 13" *9-3/4" *1/2", 7 individual Pockets, maximum 150 -200 sheets of paper. Sturdy and Portable, Easily carry and help you more effectively classify your files, papers, and documents.

LONG TERM USE: Skydue plastic folders with pockets are made of premium quality PP material, which is acid-free, PVC-free, durable, lightweight, water-resistant, keeps your documents safe and prevents your papers from slipping out.

UNIQUE DESIGN: Skydue file organizer has 5 pockets with tabs that you can label each file and colorful labels help you search and locate quickly. Upgraded elastic cord closure, making it easier to open and close

MULTI-USEFUL: Skydue accordion file folders perfect for home, office, school or travel use. It can store bills, invoices, letters, papers and other important documents, you also can use labels to easily find which your want.
body.description: SKYDUE NEW VERSION FILE FOLDER - Combines expanding file folder with pocket folder, bringing you to the new file folder world. Using the 5 Pockets file folder with 2 Pockets individual folder to become the new 7 Pockets file folder.Features of the Skydue document organizer: ① 5 pockets file folder & 2 pockets individual folder meet your storing document need ② Colorful labels help you search and locate documents quickly. ③ Made of premium quality PP material, make sure the document folder is long-time use. ④ Elastic cord closure prevents your papers from falling out.product Specifications: Material: PP & Elastic cord Color: Black Size: 13" x 9.75" x 0.5", suit for letter-size or A4 documents Capacity: No less than 200 sheets Package Include: 1 x file folder, 1 x label sticker Occasions: Home, School, Office, Travel

reviews.reviewText: This folder is unique in its design - a regular folder with a flap on each side plus an 5-slot accordian folder in the back, all held together with two secure and tight elastics.The folder is 0.5 inch thick which means it cannot hold too much paper.The plastic of the folder is smooth and flexible but it's not the really flexible, bendy plastic you would get with a plastic 3-ring binder you would get at Wal-Mart; it is rather a firm plastic.Unfortunately, the plastic of the accordian part could be more durable. It feels a bit thin.Overall, I would still recommed this folder for its very unique design and overall good build.
